===Adjective===
'''intransigent''' (alternate but rare spelling: '''intransigeant''')
# [[Stubborn]]ly unwilling to [[compromise]] or [[moderate]] a position, [[unreasonable]].
#:''Don't waste your time trying to change his mind, he's completely '''intransigent'''.''

